section_title: ANNUAL COMPILATION AND ACCOUNTING REPORT BY PROTOCOL ANNEX B PARTIES:
sentences: This issue (FCCC/KP/CMP/2009/15 and Add.1) was first addressed by the SBI plenary on 31 May.
It was referred to the contact group co-chaired by Agyemang-Bonsu and Miyagawa.
The Secretariat introduced the main findings of its second report and said the next report will be presented to COP/MOP 6 in Cancún.
The SBI did not reach conclusions on this issue and consideration of the issue will continue at SBI 33.
